- Update to v2.3.1
  New 3rd party printer profiles
  * Multiple Creality printers profiles were added (Ender-3 Max,
    Ender-4, Ender-6, CR-5 Pro, CR-5 Pro H, CR-6 SE, CR-6 Max,
    CR-10 Max, CR-200B, CR-8), thanks @pmjdebruijn.
